<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no">
  <title>编程加加</title>
  <link rel="shortcut icon" href="/img/nologo.png">
  <meta name="description" content="Scratch、Python、C++教学，竞赛、等级考试。">
  <meta name="keyword" content="Scratch,Python,C++,少儿编程,K12,来编程,中小学生创客,STEAM,小学信息技术,机器人编程,图形化编程">
  <link type="text/css" rel="stylesheet" href="/layui/css/layui.css"/>
<style>
.footer-copyright p {
  text-align: center;
  font-size: 1rem;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  
  margin-top: 80px;
  padding: 20px 0;
  background-color: #F8F8F8;
}
.father{
  display:flex;
  justify-content: center;
  align-items:center;
}
.son{
  display:flex;
  flex-direction:column;
  justify-content:center;
}
</style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="father">
    <div class="son">
      <% if (typeof(tip) != "undefined") {%>
        <i class="layui-icon layui-icon-tips" style="font-size:24px;color: #F72;"></i>
        <p style="font-size: large;"><%= tip.msg %>... 
          <% if (tip.opt == "go") {%>
          <a href="<%=tip.href%>" class="layui-btn layui-btn-sm layui-btn-primary">刷新</a>
          <%}%>
          <% if (tip.opt == "flash") {%>
          <a href="javascript:location.reload()" class="layui-btn layui-btn-sm layui-btn-primary">刷新</a>
          <%}%>
          <% if (tip.opt == "close") {%>
            <a href="javascript:window.close()" class="layui-btn layui-btn-sm layui-btn-primary">关闭本页</a>
          <%}%>            
        </p>
      <% } else {%>
        <i class="layui-icon layui-icon-404" style="font-size:404px;color: #444;"></i>
        <p>
          无权访问 或 页面数据被运到火星了，啥都看不到了...
          <a href="/" class="layui-btn layui-btn-sm layui-btn-primary">返回首页 </a>
        </p>
      <%}%>
    </div>
  </div>

<footer id="footer">
  <div class="container-fluid">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-12" style="padding: 0;">
        <div class="footer-copyright"><p>©2020. LLC. All rights reserved.编程加加</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
</body>
</html>